				<td colspan="2"><span>&quot;Bards are like cheese, we make everything better&quot; ~Catrielle(a guildie)
<br />

<br />
At high levels a bard is everything, mana regen, haste, pulls, mez, slow, debuffs...h*ll eventually our melee even becomes somewhat almost half decent.
<br />

<br />
You won't really be adding a ton to your group until lvl 32 or so but then again niether is the rest of the group really adding a whole lot either since class difference really don't start to make a difference till 30+.</span></td>
