				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: what are bards really for..<a name="26675"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 10 04 10:25 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>At level 11ish...
<br />

<br />
HEALING: Lvl 6 Song. Hymn of Restoration ----&gt; HP by 2(L6) to 14(L65).
<br />

<br />
HASTE: Lvl 10 Song. Anthem de Arms ----&gt; Attack Speed by 10%; Increase Strength by 10(L10) to 37(L65).
<br />

<br />
PULLING: Lvl 8 Song. Kelin's Lugubrious Lament ----&gt; Increase Non-frenzy Radius by 5(L8) to 60(L65); Increase Non-reaction Radius by 10(L8) to 60(L65); Pacify.
<br />

<br />
TRAIN:  Lvl 5 Song.  Selo's Accelerando ----&gt; Increase Movement Speed by 20(L5) to 65(L50)%.
<br />

<br />
AC &amp; RESISTS:  Lvl 9 Song. Elemental Rhythms ----&gt; Increase Magic Resist by 9(L9) to 37(L65); Increase Cold Resist by 9(L9) to 37(L65); Increase Fire Resist by 9(L9) to 37(L65); Increase AC by 2(L9) to 6(L65).
<br />

<br />
NUKING: Lvl 12 Song. Brusco's Boastful Bellow ----&gt; Decrease HP by 7(L12) to 33(L65).
<br />

<br />
CROWD CONTROL: Lvl 15 Song. Kelin's Lucid Lullaby ----&gt; Mesmerize between 2 and 30 levels.
<br />

<br />
So I guess the question is... what do we not do? It is up to you to decide when to use which considering type of mobs and zone.
<br />

<br />
At level 5 we are the only class with speed increase, and can take our group along to safety (/ooc TRAIN). We can also train anyone that deserved to be trained since level 5 <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
At level 6 we can help reduce the downtime with the heal song.
<br />

<br />
At level 8 we are best pullers with selo &amp; lul song combo. Yes, we can pull the Mean-o-CrushBone_Orc_01 one by one.
<br />

<br />
At level 9 we can buff up AC a bit, along with some resistances in case group runs into Mean-o-Level-8-Castermob.
<br />

<br />
At level 10 we can increase everyone DMG output with a song that gives 10% haste AND STR buff.
<br />

<br />
In all, we can fill up group's lacking roles and excell in 1 or 2.
<br />

<br />
The above Spell INFO has been copy-pasted mercylessly from EQDiva Site without Kocho's consent.
<br />

<br />
Don't boot me, Kocho.
<br />

<br />
Nilufer.
<br />

<br />
PS: We can also twist songs, having 3 up at all times. You can actually have 4, but at low level with miss notes its kinda tough. Get all instruments and practice instrument skills singing a song while AFK at PoK zone or alike zones.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
